item.title: What Is HAMACHI!?
item.dc:creator: @T3h_Hate T3h Hate
item.description:
@T3h_Hate wrote:

Hamachi is a program that allowed you to use other peoples networks and servers
for moparscape and other things aswell to download it go to…

www.hamachi.cc

The thing with Hamachi is that you have to make sure that you use capitals when people put
Capitals to join the Ham network or it will not work

such as…OwnsPkScape

you can’t just put it as ownspkscape you need to add the capitals and any number that are
supposedto be after it.

to join a server do…

and then this will pop up

This is an example not all Ham networks will be like this.

[glow=black,2,300][size=20pt]Hamachi Premium[/size][/glow]

Hamachi Premium last for 30 days and you get a free month trial with your first download.
To buy a month subscription you must have a credit card and will last for about 31 days.

With Hamachi premium you can add more servers and also you can join servers that would usually fill
up with 16 people in it can now be like 256.

You can also more Networks if you are making Hamachi Servers

Also for more help go…http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,11179.0.html
